parameters.inputSchema:
{
	"type": "object",
	"properties": {
		"Target Market": {
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Defines the audience (niche) and their specific characteristics."
		},
		"Dream Outcome": {
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Identifies the ideal result the customer desires."
		},
		"Core Problem": {
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Describes the key challenge preventing the customer from achieving their dream outcome."
		}
	},
	"required": ["Target Market", "Dream Outcome", "Core Problem"]
}

{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "DreamOutcome": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Specifies a transformative result and why it matters to the customer."
    },
    "PerceivedLikelihoodOfAchievement": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "methods": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "description": "Methods to make success seem inevitable (e.g., testimonials, guarantees)."
        }
      }
    },
    "TimeDelay": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Minimizes delays by identifying quick wins."
    },
    "EffortAndSacrifice": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "steps": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "description": "Simplifies steps to reduce perceived difficulty."
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "required": ["DreamOutcome", "PerceivedLikelihoodOfAchievement", "TimeDelay", "EffortAndSacrifice"]
}

{
	"type": "object",
	"properties": {
		"Problems": {
			"type": "array",
			"description": "List of obstacles the customer might face in achieving the desired outcome.",
			"items": {
				"type": "string"
			}
		},
		"Solutions": {
			"type": "array",
			"description": "List of solutions corresponding to each obstacle, with compelling names.",
			"items": {
				"type": "string"
			}
		}
	},
	"required": ["Problems", "Solutions"]
}

parameters.text:
=You are an excellent Business Analyst, your goal is to propose a strong guarantee that eliminates risk for the customer. Include phrases like "or your money back," or unique performance-based guarantees to boost confidence in the offer. Always make sure it is achievable and realistic to avoid over promising.

These are the High Value Low Cost Solutions/Offers (Priority Offers) : "{{ $('Priority Offers').item.json['Priority Offers'] }}"

Example Output:
"risk_guarantees":[
   {
      "guarantee_name":"Transform in 30",
      "description":"Lose at least 10 lbs in 30 days or get double your money back."
   },
   {
      "guarantee_name":"Scale Your Agency Now",
      "description":"Generate $25,000 in new revenue within 90 days, or we’ll refund your money and cover your next ad campaign up to $1,000."
   },
   {
      "guarantee_name":"Shopify Profit Accelerator",
      "description":"Hit $10,000/month in revenue within 90 days, or we’ll refund your investment and reimburse your ad spend up to $500."
   },
   {
      "guarantee_name":"Scale Your Agency Now",
      "description":"If you don’t generate $25,000 in revenue within 90 days, we’ll personally manage your lead generation for the next 30 days at no extra cost."
   },
   {
      "guarantee_name":"Fluent Fast Track",
      "description":"If you don’t feel conversationally fluent in 90 days, you’ll get free unlimited group practice sessions until you do."
   }
]

messageValues.message:
=Propose a strong guarantee that eliminates risk for the customer. Include phrases like "or your money back," or unique performance-based guarantees to boost confidence in the offer.

Here's a context for this objective: {{ $('Context and Niche').item.json['AI Context'] }}
Make use of this context as a guiding principle.

This is our Target Customer Profile: {{ $('Value Equation').item.json['Target Audience'] }}

Here's the Value Equation based on Alex Hormozi's Book:
Value = (Dream Outcome×Perceived Likelihood of Achievement)/(Time Delay+Effort and Sacrifice)

These are our Value Equation elements:
 - Dream Outcome: {{ $('Value Equation').item.json['Dream Outcome'] }}
 - Perceived Likelihood of Achievement: {{ $('Value Equation').item.json['Perceived Likelihood of Success'] }}
 - Time Delay: {{ $('Value Equation').item.json['Time Delay'] }}
 - Effort and Sacrifice: {{ $('Value Equation').item.json['Effort and Sacrifice'] }}

